# Nikolsk, Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia

}}
Nikolsk () is a rural locality (a selo) in Kabansky District, Republic of Buryatia, Russia. The population was 194 as of 2010. There are 3 streets.
Geography
Nikolsk is located 25&nbsp;km east of Kabansk (the district's administrative centre) by road. Treskovo is the nearest rural locality.
